    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >试试加入我们的群组吧：</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【QQ流动1群】236996310</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【QQ流动2群】570041439</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >↑任何疑问都可以私信管理员帮您解决，流动群会定期清人还望见谅哦~</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏简介</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Dusk Pub / 黄昏酒馆》是一款包含“美少女+模拟经营+GALGAME”的游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为黄昏酒馆的店长，你需要努力经营自己破旧的酒馆，将分店扩张至“布伦特”大陆的不同地区。期间你还会邂逅各式各样的美少女，招募她们成为你的店员，培养她们的业务能力并了解她们的全部吧。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220830/extras/64f2c40a335b791964b4184b5a75c89e.poster.avif?t=1771064545\" width=192 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220830/extras/64f2c40a335b791964b4184b5a75c89e.webm?t=1771064545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220830/extras/64f2c40a335b791964b4184b5a75c89e.mp4?t=1771064545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >轻度模拟经营</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过店员养成、店铺经营、酒馆升级、开设分店等方式赚取卢恩金币并提升酒馆声望，将破旧的酒馆做大做强，打败邪恶的资本家。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当然啦，你也可以通过赠送礼物提升妹子们的好感度，随著好感度的提升可以解锁更多关于她们的故事，了解她们的全部❥。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220830/extras/a5e0c9a2c59dcff43f97f5392bb48a39.avif?t=1771064545\" width=640 height=360 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220830/extras/067131e82cb3b2bde018d8115e1f2750.avif?t=1771064545\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >分店经营</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏将在剧情推进到一定进度时开放分店经营放置玩法，通过开设分店招募来自各地的店员，让她们不间断地为你赚取卢恩金币吧~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220830/extras/ffcfc436520474afb70cb7c57b69c85b.avif?t=1771064545\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >全程语音</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位美少女都拥有完整的中/日文配音，游戏含有大量精心绘制的CG并支援2K、4K高清解析度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220830/extras/dd132d5550d9c940d31efc12b6bd9496.avif?t=1771064545\" width=640 height=360 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >场景解谜玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过探索与美少女相关的场景推进故事发展，放心，这很简单。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220830/extras/3e3fcb013f06e06a95595e5f008ca948.avif?t=1771064545\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果您对我们的游戏感兴趣，可以<strong><u>将游戏添加进愿望单</u></strong>，能得到您的关注将让我们备感鼓舞</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ヾ(*´▽‘*)ﾉ</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220830/extras/cb228a4f49afcf64e4c3acbd48baa3b9.poster.avif?t=1771064545\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220830/extras/cb228a4f49afcf64e4c3acbd48baa3b9.webm?t=1771064545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
